{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4532b0c01b","title":"毛泽东对中南军区三反指示和谭政来电的复电和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d010e0a821","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"4532b0c01b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f67b7a9c83","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对中南军区三反指示和谭政来电的复电和批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"4ffee03eb0","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"e3f7f5d4ed","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"44bdc1c636","type":"appellation","text":"谭政同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"7cea5877c4","type":"paragraph","text":"此件及十二月三十日十五时电均阅悉。此件很好，你们对整编与三反的矛盾已大体上解决了，你们就有了主动。但有两点不妥，我已批在文内，请考虑改正。此外，请注意：（一）对各军区以电话电报严加督促，勤加指导，务使每天都有收获。（二）亲手抓紧直属部门，三天一会，五天一报，照西南的办法，做出成绩，取得经验，通报各处。盼望你们的捷报。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"72c59f164e","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月一日二时","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"213ba4d024","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"9cd141d3ed","type":"paragraph","text":"这是很对的。——毛注","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"fd66893237","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"0b0dd96fbe","type":"paragraph","text":"这一条不妥。一般机关人员从司令部政治部到连部，也有贪污人员，他们可以这一条为借口，只反浪费，不反贪污。必须使一切机关部队学校既反浪费，又反贪污，凡有贪污现象者皆须彻底肃清。——毛注","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"e28048e4ed","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"299be3ab5d","type":"paragraph","text":"这样规定不妥。各级军区和被整编部队均可以这一条为借口，注意整编不注[重]三反。应照华东规定：（一）一月份以三反为主，结合整编；二三两月以整编为主，结合三反。（二）领导干部分工，以一人专管三反，他人助之；以一人专管整编；以一人照顾其他工作；而在三反高潮时应集中大力完成三反。——毛注","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"8c054be74b","type":"appellation","text":"五","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"a09869b30c","type":"appellation","text":"林彪同志：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"57633f1a5b","type":"paragraph","text":"接到谭政此电及另一文件后，已将批评中南的电报停发，因为谭政的思想已扭转过来了。谭写的另一文件是基本正确的，有两点不妥处，我已批在文内，于今夜派专人送给谭政，并告诉他一些做法。你病如何，望好养护。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"},{"id":"2655ecc52e","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月一日上午三时","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b"}],"page":{"id":"aa0effaa3d","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"4532b0c01b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}